🛒 Amazon Clone
A front-end clone of Amazon’s homepage built using pure HTML and CSS — no JavaScript involved.

📌 Features
✅ Amazon-like Header with Logo, Search Bar, and Navigation

✅ Responsive Product Cards

✅ Fully styled Footer with links

✅ Lightweight: Pure HTML + CSS (No frameworks, no JavaScript)

🚀 How to Run the Project
Open VS Code or any code editor.

Clone this repository:
https://github.com/Allyankhan/Amazon-clone.git
using the command git clone

git clone https://github.com/Allyankhan/Amazon-clone.git
Navigate into the project folder:

cd Amazon-clone
Open with Live Server or simply open index.html in your browser.

